'''Tamil Nadu Water Supply and Drainage Board''' ('''TWAD Board''') is a public agency formed by the [[Government of Tamil Nadu]], assigned with task of providing [[water supply]] and [[sanitary sewer|sewerage]] facilities to the state of [[Tamil Nadu]] (except the [[Chennai Metropolitan Area]]). It was formed on April 14, 1971.<ref>[http://twadboard.gov.in/main_public_aboutus.html Tamil Nadu Water Supply and Drainage Board website - About us]</ref>
