'''Zalicus''' is an [[United States of America|American]] [[biomedical]] company headquartered in Cambridge, Massachusetts.  The company is finding new ways to cure pain. In 2013, Zalicus dropped Z160, a painkiller that would treat pain from shingles. The stock symbol is ZLCS. 

